VERSION 5.8 ;
DESIGN demo_chip ;
UNITS DISTANCE MICRONS 1000 ;
DIEAREA ( 0 0 ) ( 50000 50000 ) ;
COMPONENTS 3 ;
- U1 NAND2 + PLACED ( 5000 5000 ) N ;
- U2 INV + PLACED ( 15000 12000 ) FS ;
- U3 BUF + PLACED ( 30000 25000 ) N ;
END COMPONENTS
NETS 3 ;
- clk ( PIN clk ) ( U1 A ) ( U2 Z ) ;
- data_in ( PIN din ) ( U1 B ) ( U3 A ) ;
- VDD ( U1 VDD ) ( U2 VDD ) ( U3 VDD ) ;
END NETS
END DESIGN
